This is a test project for integrating the Recast navigation library (http://code.google.com/p/recastnavigation) with Ogre3D (http://www.ogre3d.org).
By Duststorm, thanks to the snippets from mkultra333 (http://www.ogre3d.org/forums/viewtopic.php?f=5&t=62079) and Paul Wilson (http://www.ogre3d.org/forums/viewtopic.php?f=11&t=57487).

Using Ogre 1.7.3 or 1.8 and Recast 1.4 (svn revision 345)


